{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_iyYA3KwuHa6dnrrGUjjS5O9d","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AnyRouter VPN proxy tool product\"\n\nSearch results for query: AnyRouter VPN proxy tool product AnyRouter proxy server setup guide AnyRouter VPN security features\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"AnyRouter 介绍\",\"url\":\"https://www.rcdfrd.com/archives/40\"},{\"title\":\"Router Proxy Setup: Step-by-Step Configuration Guide 2026\",\"url\":\"https://toproxylab.com/blog/how-to-set-up-a-proxy-on-your-router\"},{\"title\":\"Setting up a proxy server on the router - detailed instructions\",\"url\":\"https://belurk.com/blog/setting-up-proxy-on-router\"},{\"title\":\"Free Claude Code Access: AnyRouter $50 Credit Guide\",\"url\":\"https://lafucode.com/en/posts/how-to-use-claude-code-for-free\"},{\"title\":\"anyproxy 安装运行\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/keenajiao/p/15842235.html\"},{\"title\":\"AnyRouter: Claude Code API relay service for developers in restricted regions – BetterAI\",\"url\":\"https://betterai.dev/anyrouter\"},{\"title\":\"WinXP Gateway（网关）—— 基于 AnyRouter 将电脑变成软网关-CSDN博客\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/shida_csdn/article/details/85322870\"},{\"title\":\"Windows 11 下使用 Kimi K2 和 Anyrouter 驱动 Claude Code，并切换\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/geyee/p/18982151\"},{\"title\":\"AnyProxy安装使用【Windows】_anyoroxy 安装-CSDN博客\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44536804/article/details/87908388\"},{\"title\":\"Proxy Server Setup\",\"url\":\"https://docs.oracle.com/communications/E69835_01/doc.63/e69836/proxy-server-setup1.htm\"},{\"title\":\"How to Set Up a Proxy Server | Guide to Using a Proxy Server\",\"url\":\"https://www.paloaltonetworks.com/cyberpedia/how-to-set-up-a-proxy-server\"},{\"title\":\"【实操】anyproxy的安装和启动使用\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/kechen/p/12662640.html\"},{\"title\":\"anyrouter - 必应\",\"url\":\"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=anyrouter&gs_lcrp=EgRlZGdlKgcIABBFGMIDMgcIABBFGMIDMgcIARBFGMIDMgcIAhBFGMIDMgcIAxBFGMIDMgcIBBBFGMIDMgcIBRBFGMIDMgcIBhBFGMIDMgcIBxBFGMID0gEJMTkxOTRqMGo5qAIIsAIB&FORM=ANAB01&PC=U531\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - loks666/anyrouter-autolog: 🤖AnyRouter多账号签到。\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/loks666/anyrouter-autolog\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here is information about **AnyRouter** and related proxy tools. It's important to note that there are multiple distinct products with similar names, so I'll clarify each:\n\n---\n\n## 1. AnyRouter (anyrouter.top) — Claude Code API Relay Service\n\nThe most prominent current product called **AnyRouter** is **not a traditional VPN**, but rather a **third-party API relay/proxy service** specifically designed to provide access to **Anthropic's Claude Code and Claude AI models** for developers in regions with restricted access (e.g., mainland China).\n\n### Product Overview\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Primary Function** | API relay/mirror for Anthropic's Claude Code CLI and API |\n| **Target Users** | Developers who cannot directly access Anthropic's official API |\n| **Website** | `https://anyrouter.top/` |\n| **Mechanism** | Forwards requests to Anthropic's API nodes; users point their Claude Code client to AnyRouter's endpoint |\n\n### Key Features\n- **Regional Access Solution**: Allows usage of Claude Code without requiring additional international network configuration (VPNs)\n- **Easy Integration**: Works by changing two environment variables:\n  - `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://anyrouter.top`\n  - `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=<your AnyRouter API key>`\n- **Cost-Effective**: Offers shared access plans; new users reportedly receive free credits ($50–$100)\n- **Model Support**: Supports Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Claude 4.5, Claude Code with million-token context, and other Anthropic models\n- **Auto-Check-In**: Third-party tools exist for multi-account daily check-ins to earn additional credits\n\n### Usage Example\n```bash\nexport ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://anyrouter.top\nexport CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC=1\nexport ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=sk-...\nclaude\n```\n\n### ⚠️ Important Considerations\n- **Third-Party Service**: This is **not an official Anthropic product**. All API requests route through the operator's servers.\n- **Privacy/Security Risk**: Code, prompts, and sensitive data are transmitted through an intermediary. Exercise caution with proprietary code or credentials.\n- **Similar Services**: The ecosystem includes comparable relay services like CodeProxy, AIGo>Code, and Agent Router.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Legacy AnyRouter — Windows Soft Gateway Tool\n\nAn older, unrelated Windows software also named **AnyRouter** (version 2.85) exists:\n- **Function**: Turns a Windows PC (notably Windows XP) into a **soft gateway/router** for LAN sharing\n- **Use Case**: Allows other computers on a local network to share one machine's internet connection without individual proxy configuration\n- **Status**: Appears to be legacy/abandoned software from many years ago\n\n---\n\n## 3. AnyProxy — Open-Source HTTP Debugging Proxy\n\nSearch results frequently confuse **AnyRouter** with **AnyProxy**, a well-known open-source project by Alibaba:\n- **Function**: Node.js-based HTTP/HTTPS proxy server for **web traffic debugging**, request interception, and traffic capture\n- **Use Case**: Developers use it to inspect mobile app traffic, debug web requests, and modify local data returns\n- **Key Ports**: Proxy runs on `8001`, web management UI on `8002`\n- **HTTPS Support**: Requires installing a Root CA certificate to decrypt HTTPS traffic\n- **Relation to AnyRouter**: **Completely different product**; no affiliation\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nIf you are looking for the **current \"AnyRouter\" product** being discussed in developer communities, it is the **Claude Code API relay service** (`anyrouter.top`), not a general-purpose VPN or router firmware. It functions as a specialized proxy for AI coding tools rather than a full network VPN. If you need a traditional VPN or router-level proxy, you would need different solutions (such as OpenWRT-based routers, Shadowsocks, or commercial VPN services).\n\nWould you like more details on setting up the Claude Code relay, or were you looking for a different type of VPN/proxy tool?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d88e582a-137a-4477-b517-07ab0ddc91cb","uuid":"e518e87b-2a0d-4de6-b0e7-1bf855a352c6","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:48:01.899Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"AnyRouter VPN proxy tool product","results":["Search results for query: AnyRouter VPN proxy tool product AnyRouter proxy server setup guide AnyRouter VPN security features",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d87m2eiiur0s73eml4kg","content":[{"title":"AnyRouter 介绍","url":"https://www.rcdfrd.com/archives/40"},{"title":"Router Proxy Setup: Step-by-Step Configuration Guide 2026","url":"https://toproxylab.com/blog/how-to-set-up-a-proxy-on-your-router"},{"title":"Setting up a proxy server on the router - detailed instructions","url":"https://belurk.com/blog/setting-up-proxy-on-router"},{"title":"Free Claude Code Access: AnyRouter $50 Credit Guide","url":"https://lafucode.com/en/posts/how-to-use-claude-code-for-free"},{"title":"anyproxy 安装运行","url":"https://www.cnblogs.com/keenajiao/p/15842235.html"},{"title":"AnyRouter: Claude Code API relay service for developers in restricted regions – BetterAI","url":"https://betterai.dev/anyrouter"},{"title":"WinXP Gateway（网关）—— 基于 AnyRouter 将电脑变成软网关-CSDN博客","url":"https://blog.csdn.net/shida_csdn/article/details/85322870"},{"title":"Windows 11 下使用 Kimi K2 和 Anyrouter 驱动 Claude Code，并切换","url":"https://www.cnblogs.com/geyee/p/18982151"},{"title":"AnyProxy安装使用【Windows】_anyoroxy 安装-CSDN博客","url":"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44536804/article/details/87908388"},{"title":"Proxy Server Setup","url":"https://docs.oracle.com/communications/E69835_01/doc.63/e69836/proxy-server-setup1.htm"},{"title":"How to Set Up a Proxy Server | Guide to Using a Proxy Server","url":"https://www.paloaltonetworks.com/cyberpedia/how-to-set-up-a-proxy-server"},{"title":"【实操】anyproxy的安装和启动使用","url":"https://www.cnblogs.com/kechen/p/12662640.html"},{"title":"anyrouter - 必应","url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=anyrouter&gs_lcrp=EgRlZGdlKgcIABBFGMIDMgcIABBFGMIDMgcIARBFGMIDMgcIAhBFGMIDMgcIAxBFGMIDMgcIBBBFGMIDMgcIBRBFGMIDMgcIBhBFGMIDMgcIBxBFGMID0gEJMTkxOTRqMGo5qAIIsAIB&FORM=ANAB01&PC=U531"},{"title":"GitHub - loks666/anyrouter-autolog: 🤖AnyRouter多账号签到。","url":"https://github.com/loks666/anyrouter-autolog"}]},"Based on the web search results, here is information about **AnyRouter** and related proxy tools. It's important to note that there are multiple distinct products with similar names, so I'll clarify each:\n\n---\n\n## 1. AnyRouter (anyrouter.top) — Claude Code API Relay Service\n\nThe most prominent current product called **AnyRouter** is **not a traditional VPN**, but rather a **third-party API relay/proxy service** specifically designed to provide access to **Anthropic's Claude Code and Claude AI models** for developers in regions with restricted access (e.g., mainland China).\n\n### Product Overview\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Primary Function** | API relay/mirror for Anthropic's Claude Code CLI and API |\n| **Target Users** | Developers who cannot directly access Anthropic's official API |\n| **Website** | `https://anyrouter.top/` |\n| **Mechanism** | Forwards requests to Anthropic's API nodes; users point their Claude Code client to AnyRouter's endpoint |\n\n### Key Features\n- **Regional Access Solution**: Allows usage of Claude Code without requiring additional international network configuration (VPNs)\n- **Easy Integration**: Works by changing two environment variables:\n  - `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://anyrouter.top`\n  - `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=<your AnyRouter API key>`\n- **Cost-Effective**: Offers shared access plans; new users reportedly receive free credits ($50–$100)\n- **Model Support**: Supports Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Claude 4.5, Claude Code with million-token context, and other Anthropic models\n- **Auto-Check-In**: Third-party tools exist for multi-account daily check-ins to earn additional credits\n\n### Usage Example\n```bash\nexport ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://anyrouter.top\nexport CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC=1\nexport ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=sk-...\nclaude\n```\n\n### ⚠️ Important Considerations\n- **Third-Party Service**: This is **not an official Anthropic product**. All API requests route through the operator's servers.\n- **Privacy/Security Risk**: Code, prompts, and sensitive data are transmitted through an intermediary. Exercise caution with proprietary code or credentials.\n- **Similar Services**: The ecosystem includes comparable relay services like CodeProxy, AIGo>Code, and Agent Router.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Legacy AnyRouter — Windows Soft Gateway Tool\n\nAn older, unrelated Windows software also named **AnyRouter** (version 2.85) exists:\n- **Function**: Turns a Windows PC (notably Windows XP) into a **soft gateway/router** for LAN sharing\n- **Use Case**: Allows other computers on a local network to share one machine's internet connection without individual proxy configuration\n- **Status**: Appears to be legacy/abandoned software from many years ago\n\n---\n\n## 3. AnyProxy — Open-Source HTTP Debugging Proxy\n\nSearch results frequently confuse **AnyRouter** with **AnyProxy**, a well-known open-source project by Alibaba:\n- **Function**: Node.js-based HTTP/HTTPS proxy server for **web traffic debugging**, request interception, and traffic capture\n- **Use Case**: Developers use it to inspect mobile app traffic, debug web requests, and modify local data returns\n- **Key Ports**: Proxy runs on `8001`, web management UI on `8002`\n- **HTTPS Support**: Requires installing a Root CA certificate to decrypt HTTPS traffic\n- **Relation to AnyRouter**: **Completely different product**; no affiliation\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nIf you are looking for the **current \"AnyRouter\" product** being discussed in developer communities, it is the **Claude Code API relay service** (`anyrouter.top`), not a general-purpose VPN or router firmware. It functions as a specialized proxy for AI coding tools rather than a full network VPN. If you need a traditional VPN or router-level proxy, you would need different solutions (such as OpenWRT-based routers, Shadowsocks, or commercial VPN services).\n\nWould you like more details on setting up the Claude Code relay, or were you looking for a different type of VPN/proxy tool?"],"durationSeconds":56.27182957999999,"searchCount":1}}
