ader>\n    <div class=\"main\" id=\"main_title\">\n        <a href=/>rcdfrd blog</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"/\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"/posts\">All posts</a>\n        \n        \n            <a href=\"/friends.html\">友链</a>\n        \n            <a href=\"/about.html\">关于</a>\n        \n        | <form class=\"search-form\" action=\"/search/\" method=\"get\">\n            <input type=\"search\" name=\"q\" class=\"search-input\"\n                   placeholder=\"Search…\" maxlength=\"50\"\n                   value=\"\"\n                   aria-label=\"Search articles\">\n        </form>\n        | <a id=\"dark-mode-toggle\" onclick=\"toggleTheme()\" href=\"\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"\n             stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\n             class=\"feather feather-moon\">\n            <path d=\"M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z\"></path>\n        </svg>\n        </a>\n\n        <script src=\"/static/js/themetoggle.js\"></script>\n    </nav>\n</header>\n\n\n        \n    <main>\n        <article>\n            <div class=\"title\">\n                <h1 class=\"title\">AnyRouter 介绍</h1>\n                <div class=\"meta\">\n                    Published by <a target=\"_blank\">rcdfrd</a> on 2025-12-07\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <section class=\"body\">\n                <h1>AnyRouter 介绍</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://anyrouter.top/\">AnyRouter</a> 是一个第三方 Claude Code API 代理，方便在国内使用墙内网络访问。</p>\n<h2>使用方法</h2>\n<p>在终端中设置以下三个环境变量：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"><span style=\"color: #008000\">export</span><span style=\"color: #BBB\"> </span><span style=\"color: #19177C\">ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL</span><span style=\"color: #666\">=</span>https://c.cspok.cn\n<span style=\"color: #008000\">export</span><span style=\"color: #BBB\"> </span><span style=\"color: #19177C\">CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC</span><span style=\"color: #666\">=1</span>\n<span style=\"color: #008000\">export</span><span style=\"color: #BBB\"> </span><span style=\"color: #19177C\">ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN</span><span style=\"color: #666\">=</span>你的API密钥\n</code></pre>\n<h3>环境变量说明</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">变量</th>\n<th align=\"left\">作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">代理地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">设置为 <code>1</code>，让所有请求走代理</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">你在 AnyRouter 获取的密钥</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>设置完成后正常启动 Claude Code 即可。</p>\n<h2>开始之前</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>访问 <a href=\"https://anyrouter.top/\">https://anyrouter.top/</a> 注册账户</li>\n<li>获取 API 密钥</li>\n<li>配置环境变量</li>\n<li>运行 Claude Code</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>风险提示</h2>\n<p>这是一个第三方服务，并非 Anthropic 官方提供。你的请求会经过他们的服务器，请注意：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>敏感代码、密钥等信息请谨慎传输</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>先了解他们的定价策略和服务条款</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>妥善保管你的 API 密钥，避免泄露</p>\n<p>详细信息请访问官方网站查看。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n            </section>\n            <div class=\"post-tags\">\n                <nav class=\"nav tags\">\n                    <ul class=\"tags\">\n                        \n                    </ul>\n                </nav>\n            </div>\n        </article>\n    </main>\n\n\n        <footer>\n    <div class=\"footer-info\">\n        2026 © rcdfrd\n        | <a href=\"/\">rcdfrd blog</a>\n    </div>\n</footer>\n\n<script> feather.replace(); </script>\n\n<script>\n    document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function () {\n        renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n            // customised options\n            // • auto-render specific keys, e.g.:\n            delimiters: [\n                {left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},\n                {left: '$', right: '$', display: false},\n                {left: '\\\\(', right: '\\\\)', display: false},\n                {left: '\\\\[', right: '\\\\]', display: true}\n            ],\n            ignoredClasses: [\"description\"],\n            // • rendering keys, e.g.:\n            throwOnError: false\n        });\n    });\n\n</script>\n    </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d88e582a-137a-4477-b517-07ab0ddc91cb","uuid":"c28d03a8-2f2a-4448-b4a9-92ade5c33e22","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:48:59.935Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-cn\">\n\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\n    \n        <title>AnyRouter 介绍</title>\n        <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"AnyRouter 介绍\"/>\n    \n\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"A simple blog built by Django\"/>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A simple blog built by Django\"/>\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/ico\" href=\"/static/icon/favicon.ico\"/>\n\n    <script src=\"/static/js/feather.min.js\"></script>\n    \n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/static/css/normalize.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/static/css/fonts.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen\" href=\"/static/css/main.css\"/>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" id=\"darkModeStyle\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/static/css/dark.css\" disabled=true/>\n\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.8/dist/katex.min.css\"\n          integrity=\"sha384-GvrOXuhMATgEsSwCs4smul74iXGOixntILdUW9XmUC6+HX0sLNAK3q71HotJqlAn\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n    <!-- The loading of KaTeX is deferred to speed up page rendering -->\n    <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.8/dist/katex.min.js\"\n        